title: Gunmen kill Philippine town mayor, wound 4 others in south
text:
Published By: Philly News Nation/World - Today 
MANILA, Philippines (AP) - Gunmen killed a Philippine town mayor and wounded his vice mayor and at least three other companions in an ambush...
